frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T08:21:49.000Z","msg":"相信你心中一定非常痛苦，才會如此寫下你的心聲！雖然，我並未完全了解你，但我明白置身痛苦中是怎樣一回事。有些人在困苦之中，會選擇放棄自己，不知道你是否也有這自殺的念頭？<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n無論你是否想過放棄自己，我也希望你不要將困擾藏在心裡。因為人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。你不如停一停，<a href=\"http://到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%88%B0%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.help4suicide.com.hk&d=zfdFiT6AsDrEZY5hulh1d5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=4e205803\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。 那裡有一些勵志故事、有趣短片，也有與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看。您更可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"d214afc2cc0024881a8e5f9e60fa633a16e26365","tid":919943,"uid":14029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75add8a69c9f6818abf2bfb736670ba5dbdbed46","tid":919943,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86a6e6a10f8ffbe2244573efbd722f4755cedc0f","tid":919943,"uid":2756,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T12:25:19.000Z","msg":"我都系<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T12:26:02.000Z","msg":"好唔開心左幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T08:28:47.000Z","msg":"廿幾年啦起碼"},{"pid":"9edbb33facf7db4b96d34a961521d222d9414206","tid":919943,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d214afc2cc0024881a8e5f9e60fa633a16e26365","tid":919943,"uid":14029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75add8a69c9f6818abf2bfb736670ba5dbdbed46","tid":919943,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86a6e6a10f8ffbe2244573efbd722f4755cedc0f","tid":919943,"uid":2756,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T12:25